	<Title>
		Fast weight loss: What&apos;s wrong with it?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Fast weight loss &amp;mdash; Beware of trying to lose too much too soon.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Why do doctors recommend a slow rate of weight loss? What&apos;s wrong with fast weight loss?
	</Question>
